cross: Paphiopedilum fairrieanum x Paphiopedilum Pacific Shamrock

measurements.description:
One well-presented flower held well above the foliage on one inflorescence; dorsal sepal white, mid-rib dark rose, blushed and veined chartreuse centrally, dark rose veined 
   marginally; petals white, heavily overlaid chartreuse, dark rose striation stronger on margins; synsepal white
   overlaid chartreuse; pouch chartreuse, superior half lightly overlaid dark rose;  staminode chartreuse, dark rose centrally;  
   substance good; texture waxy.
